    "description": "<p>NTUC Fairprice Co-operative Limited is and will always be Singapore's very own icon. &nbsp;With a clear social mission to moderate cost of living and help Singaporeans, we have grown over the years to become Singapore's largest retailer. We are constantly transforming ourselves to serve the needs of our customers, provide them with a world-class quality shopping experience and to continue to do good for Singapore. &nbsp;In 2017, we were named Human Capital Partner by the Tripartite Alliance for Fair and Progressive Employment Practices (TAFEP) and the Ministry of Manpower (MOM). The Human Capital Partners are fair and progressive employers recognised for our exemplary human capital programmes and progressive workplace practices.</p>",
